From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mohammad Ebrahim Rahimbeiky <rahimbeiky@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 22:00:00 +0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add combat knockback profile system

Adds a dedicated reloadable combat profile at knockback/profile.yml and wires
melee knockback, projectile launch/impact, arrow impact, fishing hook impact,
and explosion velocity through one fail-safe profile loader.

diff --git a/src/main/java/com/hpfxd/pandaspigot/config/PandaSpigotConfig.java b/src/main/java/com/hpfxd/pandaspigot/config/PandaSpigotConfig.java
